<item>
            <title>[LU-326] port bug22688 to master (recovery-small.sh: FAIL: test_18b test_18b failed with 2)</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-326</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;in test_18c, it uses df to send a statfs request to OST to detect  the disconnection and reconnect to OST, for there could be cache of the statfs, then&lt;br/&gt;
the statfs request would be sent to OST then it won&apos;t detect the disconnection stat.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;for test_18b, master has fixed it by using &quot;sleep $((TIMEOUT + 2))&quot; instead of &quot;df&quot;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
